# BuildKit reads this for the operator image (build context: operators/). The
# multi-stage build COPYs only go.mod/go.sum, api/, cmd/, and internal/ — keep
# everything else out of the context so unrelated changes don't bust the layer
# cache or bloat the upload. Test files never reach `go build`, so drop them too.
bin/
cover.out
config/
hack/
test/
Dockerfile
Makefile
PROJECT
.golangci.yml
**/*_test.go
**/testdata/
